ObjectStates.Name: Notecard
ObjectStates.Description:
Select all of the cards that you want  to import into the game that you want to play solitaire. Then save them to your chest.

Open the new workshop item and open the chest (can be found under the Host tab at the top of the screen). 

You can find your saves under "Saved Objects" in the lower left corner.
